snippet.title: Amber Heard Net Worth
snippet.description: Amber Heard is an actress that was born in Austin, Texas, on April 22, 1986. Heard began dating Johnny Depp in 2012. They would get married in a secret ceremony on February 4, 2017. Heard and Depp currently do not have any children together. After appearing in several music videos, Amber Heard got her film career started in 2004 when she earned a small role in the film "Friday Night Lights." She would quickly earn small roles in the films "North Country" and "Alpha Dog." After accepting small film and television roles for four years, Amber Heard would get her first major roles in 2008 in "Never Back Down" and "Pineapple Express." Thanks to the exposure gained from these two films, Amber Heard's acting career was starting to take off. She officially became a major star in 2011 when she earned starring roles in the films "Drive Angry" and "The Rum Diary." Heard would also get a starring role on the short-lived television show "The Playboy Club" in 2011. She was able to use her new success to earn roles in "Paranoia," "3 Days to Kill," "Machete Kills" and "Magic Mike XXL." Amber Heard currently has an estimated net worth of $4.5 million. Almost all of Heard's net worth was acquired from her film career. She did a total of four films in 2013 and 2014. The salaries Amber Heard earned for her films in the last two years are not currently known by the public.-~-~~-~~~-~~-~-Please watch: "20,000 Subscriber Giveaway!
